7. Productivity (Too many technologies to explore, not much time available)</pre><h3 style="padding:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin:1.833em 0px 0.611em;font-weight:normal;font-size:1.286em;line-height:1.222em;color:rgb(17, 17, 17);">Sed Pattern Format 6: /PATTERN/,/PATTERN/</h3><p style="margin:0px;padding:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-bottom:26px;">Prints the section of file between two regular expression (including the matched line ).<br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word;"></br><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word;"><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word;"></br>
